    variants (modulo AC)
    1. S     = S.28
       ns    = ns.31
       pkC   = pkC.33
       pms   = pms.34
       signature
             = signature.37
       z     = verify(signature.37, <'32', h(<'32', ns.31, S.28, pms.34>)>,
